CAVEATS:
- you need to call AB_Job_CheckAvailability() after creating a job


- generic settings
  - bank code
  - bank name
  - hbci version
  - bank url
  - flags:
    - userId == customerId

- settings in DDV mode:
  - flags:
    - bankDoesntSign
    - bankUsesSignSeq

- settings in RDH mode
  - rdh version
  - keysize
  - flags:
    - bankDoesntSign
    - bankUsesSignSeq
  

- settings in pin/tan mode
  - http version
  - flags
    - forceSslv3
    - noBase64
    - omitSmsAccount


